{
  "texts": [
    "18 Manne Program Attendance.",
    "To the FJC data we have added the record of attendance by all federal judges to the Manne program.",
    "Butler (1999) contains a list of all the judges that had attended through 1998, when the program as such ended (other economics trainings continued but were on more specic topics, e.g.",
    "antitrust, or were smaller in scale, e.g. 2-3 day workshops).",
    "We supplemented this list with exact years of attendance from annual reports obtained by FOIA requests and through correspondence with the Law and Economics Center at George Mason University."
  ]
}